/* Table: "BC_BoothStatusCode" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "BC_BoothStatusCode"
(
"BoothStatusID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"StatusCode" VARCHAR(20) not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
constraint PK_BC_BOOTHSTATUSCODE primary key ("BoothStatusID")
);

comment on column "BC_BoothStatusCode"."StatusCode" is

20:已创建、
30:已提交审批、
40:已审批完成、
50:方案废除';

comment on column "BC_BoothStatusCode"."Enable" is
'1:有效 0:无效';
